        <thought>Violence_Pacifism</thought>
      </li>
      <li Class="PreceptComp_KnowsMemoryThought">
        <eventDef>UsedHarmfulAbility</eventDef>
        <thought>Violence_Know_Pacifism</thought>
      </li>
      <li Class="PreceptComp_SelfTookMemoryThought">
